metadata.name: Friendzone
metadata.description:
In this world, there is a certain form of relationship. that once you become attached, you are unable to go forward or backward. That kind of relationship is "Friend Zone."

The story of two best friends but one friend wants to be more than just friends. Even though, she knows that there is no way to step up their relationship but she did not regret her friendship.

“I’m happy to be here. You are so cute. How can I not to fall in love with you?”

*The stories don't match up with the main lore of the characters.
